<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112589-0014 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 139512 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 25, 1989, Saturday, San Diego County Edition 
