Golden West (6-0) at home. It was the third time the Rustlers have scored more 
than 100 points in a game. Shwana Armstrong and Claudette Jackson scored 14 
each, Bits Sirchia had 13, Cossette Smith 12 and Danielle Barlow 10 for Golden 
West. The Rustlers led, 56-11, at the half. 
</P>
<P>
College of the Canyons 81, Fullerton College 51 -- Angie Nelson led Fullerton 
(3-2) with 15 points. Michelle Cabaldon and Tresssie Millender led Canyons 
(4-1) with 17 points each. 
</P>
