gathered in Prague square to hear speeches by Alexander Dubcek and others. UPI 
/ Reuters; Photo, Soviet tanks are shown moving into Prague's Wenceslas Square 
in 1968 as troops took over the city. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
