POSSESSIONS; SOUTH AFRICA -- GOVERNMENT; BLACKS -- SOUTH AFRICA; SOUTH AFRICA 
-- LAWS; NEIGHBORHOODS; HOUSING -- SOUTH AFRICA; DE KLERK, FREDERIK W 
</P>
