<HEADLINE>
<P>
DUTCH RAID DRUG LAB, ARREST FOUR PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
AMSTERDAM 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dutch police have raided a large drug laboratory in the southern Netherlands, 
seizing 4.7 gallons of amphetamine oil and arresting four people, a spokesman 
said Friday. 
</P>
<P>
The oil, used to make amphetamine powder, could have produced illegal drugs 
with a street value of about $300,000, the spokesman said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
