four hours of shopping at the Glendale Galleria. They drove down from 
Lancaster. ; Photo, COLOR, Child eyes items at mall. MIKE MEADOWS / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Ryan, left, and Shaun Rundle, ages 7 and 6, go over their wish 
lists with Santa Claus at Glendale Galleria. MICHAEL YBARRA 
</P>
